text: mariyu mi strilu rtusravapu vayas'su gadici poyinavaraite leka miku danini gurinci elanti anumanam unte; leka vari rtusravam inka prarambham kani varaite, alanti vari gaduvu mudu masalu. Mariyu garbhavatulaina strila gaduvu vari kanpu ayye varaku. Mariyu allah patla bhayabhaktulu galavaniki ayana, atani vyavaharanlo saulabhyam kaligistadu
